<emphasis id="5EA59F19FF92FFCCF953AEB58332FE11" box="[806,855,475,501]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">et al</emphasis>
. 2019
</bibRefCitation>
). Although 
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFF92FFCCFE55AEB58512FE11" author="Ramos-Porto, M. &amp; Coelho, P. A." box="[1056,1399,475,501]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" pagination="93 - 111" refId="ref74526" refString="Ramos-Porto, M. &amp; Coelho, P. A. (1990) Sinopse dos crustaceos decapodos Brasileiros. Anais da Sociedade Nordestina de Zoologia, 3, 93 - 111." type="journal article" year="1990">Ramos-Porto &amp; Coelho (1990)</bibRefCitation>
reports the species to the Guianas and to the entire coast of northeastern 
<collectingCountry id="14C6039BFF92FFCCF9D0AE918389FDFD" box="[933,1004,511,537]" name="Brazil" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, no records of material examined were found for the Guianas and the 
<collectingRegion id="AE158DE9FF92FFCCFB89AD4D8216FDD9" box="[508,627,547,573]" country="Brazil" name="Piaui" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Piauí state</collectingRegion>
(
<collectingCountry id="14C6039BFF92FFCCF8F0AD4D82AAFDDA" box="[645,719,547,574]" name="Brazil" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Brazil</collectingCountry>
). Sequences accession number (GenBank): CCDB 3404—16S (
<accessionNumber id="7382DEE8FF92FFCCFAEAAD288144FD85" box="[159,289,582,609]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/MF490225" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">MF490225</accessionNumber>
), COI (
<accessionNumber id="7382DEE8FF92FFCCFB06AD298196FD85" box="[371,499,583,609]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/MF490128" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">MF490128</accessionNumber>
) (
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFF92FFCCF87CAD298362FD85" author="Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Terossi, M. &amp; Negri, M. &amp; Buranelli, R. C. &amp; Robles, R. &amp; Magalhaes, T. &amp; Tamburus, A. F. &amp; Rossi, N. &amp; Miyazaki, M. J." box="[521,775,583,609]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" pagination="805 - 815" refId="ref68637" refString="Mantelatto, F. L., Terossi, M., Negri, M., Buranelli, R. C., Robles, R., Magalhaes, T., Tamburus, A. F., Rossi, N. &amp; Miyazaki, M. J. (2018) DNA sequence database as a tool to identify decapod crustaceans on the Sao Paulo coastline. Mitochondrial DNA Part A: DNA Mapping, Sequencing and Analysis, 29 (5), 805 - 815. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 24701394.2017.1365848" type="journal article" year="2018">
Mantelatto 
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FF92FFCCF8FEAD2982D9FD85" box="[651,700,583,609]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">et al</emphasis>
. 2018
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
